  ],
  "remarks": "Sergey Dregval is the General Director and Chairman of the Management Board of PJSC Inter RAO, which is one of Russia’s largest energy companies and which is controlled by the Government of the Russian Federation. Shareholders of PJSC Inter RAO include Rosneftgaz, one of the largest dividend payers to the budget of the Russian Federation. PJSC Inter RAO is the main importer/exporter of electricity in Russia. In his capacity as its General Director, Sergey Dregval is tasked with ensuring the source of revenue to the state which allows the financing of aggression against Ukraine.",
